OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and mainly sunny and
OL,6,Fbecoming very warm or hot. Some early
OL,7,Flow cloud possible, mainly through the
OL,8,FCentral Belt, but this soon clearing.
OL,9,FLight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a fine end to the
OL,12,Fday and staying dry and mainly clear
OL,13,Fovernight. Occasional low cloud may
OL,14,Ffilter through from the east. Winds
OL,15,Fremaining light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FAny low cloud soon clearing
OL,18,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,19,Fsunny spells. Temperatures down a bit,
OL,20,Fbut still warm or very warm in any
OL,21,Fsunshine. Light northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
